                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d36">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Conger</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Blaine</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rio de Janeiro</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1891-11-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 23, 1891</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Conger reports that Mr. Peixoto, the vice-president, was peacefully installed
                    in lieu of President Deodora, whose resignation was demanded by the navy, and
                    that no disturbance has followed.</p>
            </div>
